description:
Two Veterans team up with two HUGE titted rookies for 36 minutes of Non-Scripted real hardcore wrestling at its best!
Ariel X (4th) and Ava Devine (14th) take on Darling (5th) and Carly Parker (16th) in a brutal Tag Team match up. On paper it looks like a close match but one team wanted it more, one team had more experience, but one team had a mad crazed sexual creature of nature called Ava Devine.
One of the most intense out of control rd4's we have ever filmed. The losing team gets sexually pummeled by the winners, this one round is worth the price of a membership all by itself!
title: TAG TEAM
